story.text: Still sick. Even went to the doctor. Fairly certain they misdiagnosed me, but not much of a way to tell. I suppose only time can do that.
Going to eat with Elissa and Jimmy tonight in Red Lodge. Yippee. Hope I can withstand the pressure to have wine.
Also. Carol is pissed at me. Oops.
